  "detailed_description": "<strong>Hero Guider</strong> is a construction puzzle game. In the game the player is required to build a various facilities to connect the roads in order to help the hero go through the maze.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >USE LIMITED RESOURCES TO CONNECT THE ROADS</h2>In each stage there are a limited number of resources that can be used for construction. Use these resources to connect the roads so that the hero can go through the maze. Don’t be afraid of failure since that you can try as many times as you want until you succeed.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/f1af1a9897795a3cd9248010e3e1e7ec.poster.avif?t=1726728759\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/f1af1a9897795a3cd9248010e3e1e7ec.webm?t=1726728759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/f1af1a9897795a3cd9248010e3e1e7ec.mp4?t=1726728759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TAKE ADVANTAGE OF VARIOUS MECHANISMS</h2>There are many interesting mechanisms in the game. Characters can jump over obstacles using springboards, teleport through portals, and so on. Enter the game and explore more content!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/5758737012c0979e02dfc3b819db3128.poster.avif?t=1726728759\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/5758737012c0979e02dfc3b819db3128.webm?t=1726728759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/5758737012c0979e02dfc3b819db3128.mp4?t=1726728759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/cd7cd44a34eaed7701e4c324f39f7ab9.poster.avif?t=1726728759\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/cd7cd44a34eaed7701e4c324f39f7ab9.webm?t=1726728759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/cd7cd44a34eaed7701e4c324f39f7ab9.mp4?t=1726728759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >50 PUZZLES TO SOLVE</h2>50 well-designed levels from easy to difficult are waiting for you to solve. The first few levels are easy for players to solve with guidance. As the game progresses, the puzzles will become more and more difficult to meet the requirements of all puzzle lovers.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Hero Guider</strong> is a construction puzzle game. In the game the player is required to build a various facilities to connect the roads in order to help the hero go through the maze.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >USE LIMITED RESOURCES TO CONNECT THE ROADS</h2>In each stage there are a limited number of resources that can be used for construction. Use these resources to connect the roads so that the hero can go through the maze. Don’t be afraid of failure since that you can try as many times as you want until you succeed.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/f1af1a9897795a3cd9248010e3e1e7ec.poster.avif?t=1726728759\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/f1af1a9897795a3cd9248010e3e1e7ec.webm?t=1726728759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/f1af1a9897795a3cd9248010e3e1e7ec.mp4?t=1726728759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TAKE ADVANTAGE OF VARIOUS MECHANISMS</h2>There are many interesting mechanisms in the game. Characters can jump over obstacles using springboards, teleport through portals, and so on. Enter the game and explore more content!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/5758737012c0979e02dfc3b819db3128.poster.avif?t=1726728759\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/5758737012c0979e02dfc3b819db3128.webm?t=1726728759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/5758737012c0979e02dfc3b819db3128.mp4?t=1726728759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/cd7cd44a34eaed7701e4c324f39f7ab9.poster.avif?t=1726728759\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/cd7cd44a34eaed7701e4c324f39f7ab9.webm?t=1726728759\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083520/extras/cd7cd44a34eaed7701e4c324f39f7ab9.mp4?t=1726728759\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >50 PUZZLES TO SOLVE</h2>50 well-designed levels from easy to difficult are waiting for you to solve. The first few levels are easy for players to solve with guidance. As the game progresses, the puzzles will become more and more difficult to meet the requirements of all puzzle lovers.",
